trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see langword="Command" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Fornece dados para o evento de <see langword="Command" /> .

trans-unit.source: The `Command` event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control button in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> object is clicked.
trans-unit.target: O `Command` é gerado quando um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, ou <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> botão controle em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> objeto é clicado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs> class is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> methods to access information about the event that was raised.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs> classe é usada internamente pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> métodos para acessar informações sobre o evento que foi gerado.

trans-unit.source: For a list of initial property values for an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs> class, see the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs> constructor.
trans-unit.target: Para obter uma lista de valores de propriedade inicial para uma instância do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs> de classe, consulte o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs> construtor.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to handle events, see [NIB: Consuming Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre como manipular eventos, consulte [NIB: consumindo eventos](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67).
